# NeoVim Lua Basics
source: https://alpha2phi.medium.com/neovim-init-lua-e80f4f136030
see ':h lua'

## Global, Buffer, and Window Scoped Options
see ':h vim.o'
vim.o:   get or set EDITOR options
vim.bo:  get or set BUFFER-scoped local-options
vim.wo:  get or set WINDOW-scoped local-options

## Lua-Vimscript Bridge 
see ':h lua-vimscript' for defined interfaces to Vimscript and variables.
vim.call:   invokes vim-funciton or user-function {func} with arguments {...}
vim.cmd:    invokes an Ex command (the ":" commands, Vimscript statements)
vim.fn:     invokes vim-function or user-function {func} with arguments {...}

## Lua Vim Variables
see ':h lua-vim-variables'
vim.g:      global editor variables
vim.b:      buffer-scoped variables
vim.w:      window-scoped variables
vim.t:      tabpage-scoped variables

